{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/Kubernetes/Virtual Machine를 이용한 쿠버네티스 실습 환경 구축/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Woo's Dev Log","author":"nickhealthy","siteUrl":"https://nickhealthy.github.io","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"nickhealthy/nickhealthy.github.io"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":""}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"f8889f67-085e-5b83-b8d2-fdcf08fe7ecb","excerpt":"설치과정 1 Control plane VM: 쿠버네티스 클러스터를 관리하는 관리자 마스터 노드가 이 역할을 가진다. 2 스왑 메모리 비활성화 iptables가 브리지 된 트래픽을 보게하기 br_netfilter 활성화 Make sure that the  module is loaded. This can be done by running . To load it explicitly call . bridged traffic 활성화 docker 설치 및 부팅 시 docker-engine…","html":"<h2 id=\"설치과정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98%EA%B3%BC%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"설치과정 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>설치과정</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/66216102/106359524-ba5e1f80-6356-11eb-9390-1c51569b858e.PNG\" alt=\"1\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Control plane VM: 쿠버네티스 클러스터를 관리하는 관리자</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>마스터 노드가 이 역할을 가진다.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/66216102/106359526-bb8f4c80-6356-11eb-86b1-0dfa5b95a733.PNG\" alt=\"2\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"스왑-메모리-비활성화\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%8A%A4%EC%99%91-%EB%A9%94%EB%AA%A8%EB%A6%AC-%EB%B9%84%ED%99%9C%EC%84%B1%ED%99%94\" aria-label=\"스왑 메모리 비활성화 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>스왑 메모리 비활성화</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> swapoff -a\n\n\n$ <span class=\"token function\">vi</span> /etc/fstab 에서 swap.img 관련된 명령어 주석 처리</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"iptables가-브리지-된-트래픽을-보게하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#iptables%EA%B0%80-%EB%B8%8C%EB%A6%AC%EC%A7%80-%EB%90%9C-%ED%8A%B8%EB%9E%98%ED%94%BD%EC%9D%84-%EB%B3%B4%EA%B2%8C%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"iptables가 브리지 된 트래픽을 보게하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>iptables가 브리지 된 트래픽을 보게하기</h2>\n<h3 id=\"br_netfilter-활성화\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#br_netfilter-%ED%99%9C%EC%84%B1%ED%99%94\" aria-label=\"br_netfilter 활성화 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>br_netfilter 활성화</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Make sure that the <code class=\"language-text\">br_netfilter</code> module is loaded. This can be done by running <code class=\"language-text\">lsmod | grep br_netfilter</code>. To load it explicitly call <code class=\"language-text\">sudo modprobe br_netfilter</code>.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> modprobe br_netfilter</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"bridged-traffic-활성화\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#bridged-traffic-%ED%99%9C%EC%84%B1%ED%99%94\" aria-label=\"bridged traffic 활성화 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>bridged traffic 활성화</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">cat</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;&lt;</span><span class=\"token string\">EOF<span class=\"token bash punctuation\"> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">tee</span> /etc/modules-load.d/k8s.conf</span>\nbr_netfilter\nEOF</span>\n\n<span class=\"token function\">cat</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;&lt;</span><span class=\"token string\">EOF<span class=\"token bash punctuation\"> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">tee</span> /etc/sysctl.d/k8s.conf</span>\nnet.bridge.bridge-nf-call-ip6tables = 1\nnet.bridge.bridge-nf-call-iptables = 1\nEOF</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> sysctl --system</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"docker-설치-및-부팅-시-docker-engine-자동-실행-설정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#docker-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98-%EB%B0%8F-%EB%B6%80%ED%8C%85-%EC%8B%9C-docker-engine-%EC%9E%90%EB%8F%99-%EC%8B%A4%ED%96%89-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"docker 설치 및 부팅 시 docker engine 자동 실행 설정 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>docker 설치 및 부팅 시 docker-engine 자동 실행 설정</h2>\n<h3 id=\"set-up-the-repository\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#set-up-the-repository\" aria-label=\"set up the repository permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>SET UP THE REPOSITORY</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>도커 설치</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt-get</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n    apt-transport-https <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n    ca-certificates <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">curl</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n    gnupg-agent <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n    software-properties-common</code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>Docker’s official GPG key 등록</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">curl</span> -fsSL https://download.docker.com/linux/ubuntu/gpg <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> apt-key <span class=\"token function\">add</span> -\n\n$ <span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> apt-key fingerprint 0EBFCD88</code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>stable repository 등록</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> add-apt-repository <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n   <span class=\"token string\">\"deb [arch=amd64] https://download.docker.com/linux/ubuntu \\\n   <span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">$(</span>lsb_release -cs<span class=\"token variable\">)</span></span> \\\n   stable\"</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"install-docker-engine\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#install-docker-engine\" aria-label=\"install docker engine permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>INSTALL DOCKER ENGINE</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>도커 엔진 설치</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt-get</span> update\n$ <span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt-get</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> docker-ce docker-ce-cli containerd.io</code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>부팅 시 docker-engine 자동 실행</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ sudo systemctl enable docker</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"고정-ip-설정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B3%A0%EC%A0%95-ip-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"고정 ip 설정 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>고정 IP 설정</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>아이피 설정 창으로 이동</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">vi</span> /etc/netplan/00-installer-config.yaml</code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>IP를 고정으로 설정</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">network:\n  ethernets:\n    enp0s3:\n      addresses: <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">192.168</span>.219.144/24<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n      gateway4: <span class=\"token number\">192.168</span>.219.1\n      nameservers:\n        addresses: <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">8.8</span>.8.8, <span class=\"token number\">168.126</span>.63.1<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n  version: <span class=\"token number\">2</span></code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">enp0s3</code>은 사용자마다 다를 수 있으므로 <code class=\"language-text\">ifconfig</code> or <code class=\"language-text\">ip addr</code> 명렁어로 확인</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"쿠버네티스-설치\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%BF%A0%EB%B2%84%EB%84%A4%ED%8B%B0%EC%8A%A4-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\" aria-label=\"쿠버네티스 설치 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>쿠버네티스 설치</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>쿠버네티스 공식 홈페이지에 있는 명령어</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt-get</span> update <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;&amp;</span> <span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt-get</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> -y apt-transport-https <span class=\"token function\">curl</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">curl</span> -s https://packages.cloud.google.com/apt/doc/apt-key.gpg <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> apt-key <span class=\"token function\">add</span> -\n<span class=\"token function\">cat</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;&lt;</span><span class=\"token string\">EOF<span class=\"token bash punctuation\"> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">tee</span> /etc/apt/sources.list.d/kubernetes.list</span>\ndeb https://apt.kubernetes.io/ kubernetes-xenial main\nEOF</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt-get</span> update\n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt-get</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> -y kubelet kubeadm kubectl\n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> apt-mark hold kubelet kubeadm kubectl</code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>위 명령어를 한줄씩 입력해도 되지만 한번에 실행되기 위해서 스크립트 형식으로 바꾼 내용은 아래에 있다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>위의 명령어를 <code class=\"language-text\">cat</code> 명령어로 하나의 쉘 스크립트 안에 덮어쓰기</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">cat</span> <span class=\"token operator\">></span> install_kubernetes.sh\n\n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt-get</span> update <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;&amp;</span> <span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt-get</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> -y apt-transport-https curlcurl -s https://packages.cloud.google.com/apt/doc/apt-key.gpg <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> apt-key <span class=\"token function\">add</span> -cat <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;&lt;</span>EOF <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">tee</span> /etc/apt/sources.list.d/kubernetes.listdeb https://apt.kubernetes.io/ kubernetes-xenial mainEOFsudo <span class=\"token function\">apt-get</span> updatesudo <span class=\"token function\">apt-get</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> -y kubelet kubeadm kubectlsudo apt-mark hold kubelet kubeadm kubectl</code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">chmod</code> 명령어로 파일에 대한 실행 권한을 준 뒤 실행</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">chmod</span> +x ./install_kubernetes.sh\n\n$ <span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> ./install_kubernetes.sh</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"워커-노드-설정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9B%8C%EC%BB%A4-%EB%85%B8%EB%93%9C-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"워커 노드 설정 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>워커 노드 설정</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>VM에 있는 Clone 기능을 이용해 마스터 노드와 동일한 환경상태를 갖는다.</li>\n<li>워커 노드의 호스트 명과 네트워크도 동일하기 때문에 이를 바꾸어 주어야 한다.</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">vi</span> /etc/hostname\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 접속 후 원하는 호스트명 입력</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">vi</span> /etc/netplan/00-installer-config.yaml\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 네트워크 ip 주소 변경</span></code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>이때, <strong>포트포워딩도 따로 설정해 주어야 함</strong></p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">reboot</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"클러스터-생성\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%81%B4%EB%9F%AC%EC%8A%A4%ED%84%B0-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\" aria-label=\"클러스터 생성 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>클러스터 생성</h2>\n<p><strong>하나의 쿠버네티스를 제어하는 영역을 만드는 과정</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Control plane VM에 해당함</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>쿠버네티스 클러스터를 관리하는 관리자</strong></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> kubeadm init --apiserver-advertise-address<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"10.0.2.4\"</span> --apiserver-cert-extra-sans<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"10.0.2.4\"</span> --node-name <span class=\"token string\">\"master\"</span> --pod-network-cidr<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">172.16</span>.0.0/16</code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">--apiserver-advertise-address</code>의 IP는 VM IP입니다.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">--apiserver-cert-extra-sans</code>의 IP는 VM IP입니다.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">--pod-network-cidr</code>는 쿠버네티스에 설치될 컨테이너 IP대역입니다. 조금 있다 설치할 CNI 네트워크 대역을 피하기 위해 172.16.0.0/16로 설정합니다. 만약 192.168.0.x대역으로 하면 CNI와 충돌나서 다시 클러스터를 생성해야 합니다.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>설치 이후 커맨드 창에 이러한 명령어를 실행하라고 나온다. 그대로 명령어를 실행해 주면 된다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">mkdir</span> -p <span class=\"token environment constant\">$HOME</span>/.kube\n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">cp</span> -i /etc/kubernetes/admin.conf <span class=\"token environment constant\">$HOME</span>/.kube/config\n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">chown</span> <span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">$(</span><span class=\"token function\">id</span> -u<span class=\"token variable\">)</span></span><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">:</span><span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">$(</span><span class=\"token function\">id</span> -g<span class=\"token variable\">)</span></span> <span class=\"token environment constant\">$HOME</span>/.kube/config</code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">.kube</code> 디렉토리와 <code class=\"language-text\">config</code> 파일을 홈 디렉토리에 생성</p>\n<ul>\n<li>클러스터에 들어가기 위한 인증정보들</li>\n<li><strong>config 파일이 있거나 토큰 값을 이용해 클러스터에 접속이 가능하다.</strong></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"클러스터에-워커-노드를-추가\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%81%B4%EB%9F%AC%EC%8A%A4%ED%84%B0%EC%97%90-%EC%9B%8C%EC%BB%A4-%EB%85%B8%EB%93%9C%EB%A5%BC-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80\" aria-label=\"클러스터에 워커 노드를 추가 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>클러스터에 워커 노드를 추가</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>마스터 노드에 클러스터를 생성한 이후에 나오는 <strong>토큰 값</strong> 그대로 입력 및 적용</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> 토큰 값</code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>\n<p>마스터 노드에서 확인이 가능</p>\n<ul>\n<li>클러스터에 워커 노드를 추가</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ kubectl get nodes</code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>하지만 아직 STATUS는 NOT READY 상태로 나온다. 이는 서로 통신이 안되는 상태이다.</p>\n<p>이럴 때 <strong>CNI</strong>를 설치해주어야 한다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"cni-설치calico\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#cni-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98calico\" aria-label=\"cni 설치calico permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>CNI 설치(CALICO)</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>공식 홈페이지의 명령어 입력 및 yaml 파일을 통한 설치</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">curl</span> https://docs.projectcalico.org/manifests/calico.yaml -O\n$ kubectl apply -f callico.yaml</code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>\n<p>다음의 명령어를 통해 <code class=\"language-text\">callico</code> 파드가 실행중인 것을 확인</p>\n<ul>\n<li>시간이 조금 소모되며, RUNNING 상태로 변경되면 완료된 것이다.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ kubectl get pod -n kube-system</code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>아래의 명령어로 STATUS 상태가 READY로 바뀐 것을 확인</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ kubectl get no</code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>no 는 노드를 뜻함.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>이렇게해서 쿠버네티스가 모두 설치 완료되었다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"별첨---contrlplane-vm에서-조인-명령어를-생성할-수-있다\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%B3%84%EC%B2%A8---contrlplane-vm%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-%EC%A1%B0%EC%9D%B8-%EB%AA%85%EB%A0%B9%EC%96%B4%EB%A5%BC-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1%ED%95%A0-%EC%88%98-%EC%9E%88%EB%8B%A4\" aria-label=\"별첨   contrlplane vm에서 조인 명령어를 생성할 수 있다 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>별첨 - contrlplane VM에서 조인 명령어를 생성할 수 있다.</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> kubeadm token create --print-join-command</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"reference\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#reference\" aria-label=\"reference permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Reference</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://kubernetes.io/docs/setup/production-environment/tools/kubeadm/install-kubeadm/\">https://kubernetes.io/docs/setup/production-environment/tools/kubeadm/install-kubeadm/</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://docs.docker.com/engine/install/ubuntu/\">https://docs.docker.com/engine/install/ubuntu/</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://docs.projectcalico.org/getting-started/kubernetes/self-managed-onprem/onpremises\">https://docs.projectcalico.org/getting-started/kubernetes/self-managed-onprem/onpremises</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://blog.naver.com/kgg1959/222170803683\">https://blog.naver.com/kgg1959/222170803683</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2-ebS1NuTW8&#x26;t=46s\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2-ebS1NuTW8&#x26;t=46s</a></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Virtual Machine를 이용한 쿠버네티스 실습 환경 구축","date":"January 30, 2021","category":"🧭 Kubernetes"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/Kubernetes/Virtual Machine를 이용한 쿠버네티스 실습 환경 구축/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/docker/Practice - 데이터베이스(MySQL)와 장고 연결하기/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Practice - 데이터베이스(MySQL)와 장고 연결하기","category":"🐳 docker","draft":false}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/docker/Docker network/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"도커 네트워크","category":"🐳 docker","draft":false}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3128451518","521680639"]}